Building Bitcoin on Linux! Ubuntu 14


Currently NanoCheeZe can be easily compiled and ran on Ubuntu 14.04 by bashing the install script.
sudo bash ~/NanoCheeZe/build_nc

enter password or type Y if prompted...

It's that easy!


For Windows
Download Windows the exe from http://nanocheeze.com/NanoCheeZe-qt.exe
gitian compile instructions for windows exe build coming soon...